OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning with a little
OL,6,Fdrizzle at first then a dry afternoon
OL,7,Fwith bright or sunny spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping. Becoming rather warm
OL,9,Finland but cooler along the east coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA bright end to the day then
OL,12,Fremaining dry overnight with long
OL,13,Fclear spells. Becoming rather chilly
OL,14,Fovernight with some patchy mist
OL,15,Fdeveloping.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FEarly mist soon clearing then
OL,18,Fa dry day with long spells of
OL,19,Fsunshine. Becoming quite warm inland
OL,20,Fbut cooler with some mist along the
OL,21,Feast coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
